Package phylo3D.trees

This package contains all the main data structure classes i.e. trees and their nodes.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
NodeData Abstract class representing the data in a node
NodeDataNCBI Class representing a node in the NCBI tree of life i.e. a combination of the data from the siblingGroups table with the data from the names table.
NodeDataNH Class acting as a data holder for the nodes of an TreeNH.
NodeDataNHX Class acting as a data holder for the nodes of TreeNHX
NodeDataWalrus Class representing a Node in Walrus tree.
SpecialNodes NCBI Taxonomy IDs for the special nodes in the tree of life
Tree Class representing a Tree implemented using a Hashtable.
TreeNCBI Class is data structure for the NCBI taxonomy information
TreeNH Class is a data structure for holding phylogenetic information that is to be output in NH format
TreeNHX Class is a data structure for holding phylogenetic information that is to be output in NHX format
TreeWalrus Class implementing functionality for printing out a LibSea format representation of TreeNCBI so that the TreeNCBI can be visualised using the hyperbolic tree visualisation program Walrus.
 

Package phylo3D.trees Description

This package contains all the main data structure classes i.e. trees and their nodes.
